  "Emilio Azcárraga Jean inherited control of Mexico's largest television company, Televisa, after his father, Emilio Azcarraga Milmo, died in 1997.",
  "Televisa was founded by his grandfather, Emilio Azcárraga Vidaurrieta.",
  "After two decades at the helm, Azcárraga decided to step down as Televisa's CEO at the beginning of 2018, but retains his role as chairman."
